Liverpool Corn Market.-Wheat closes firm, good business done, occasionally d.
                        dearer. Californian, No. 1 7s. 4d. to 7s. 5d. Flour : retail business;
                        steady. Oats easy. Meal quiet. Maize easier; new mixed American 4s. 2/d.;
                        Odessa 4s. 5d. Peas 6s. Saide Beans 27s. 3d, per qr. The market has a
                        holiday appearance.
